title: Untitled
content:
import requests
import pandas as pd
import json
from datetime import datetime, timedelta
import time

# –£–∫–∞–∂–∏—Ç–µ —Å–≤–æ–∏ –¥–∞–Ω–Ω—ã–µ
ACCESS_TOKEN = 'auth_token:–≤–∞—à_—Ç–æ–∫–µ–Ω_–∑–¥–µ—Å—å'  # –ó–∞–º–µ–Ω–∏—Ç–µ –Ω–∞ –≤–∞—à —Ç–æ–∫–µ–Ω
PROJECT_ID = 'lentaru'  # –ó–∞–º–µ–Ω–∏—Ç–µ –Ω–∞ –≤–∞—à project_id
PROJECT_NAME = 'Lenta.ru'  # –ó–∞–º–µ–Ω–∏—Ç–µ –Ω–∞ –≤–∞—à–µ project_name
DATE = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=1)).strftime('%Y-%m-%d')  # –í—á–µ—Ä–∞—à–Ω—è—è –¥–∞—Ç–∞
SCHEDULE_TASK_URL = 'https://api.vp.rambler.ru/api/v3/stats/scheduleTask'
SCHEDULED_RESULTS_URL = 'https://api.vp.rambler.ru/api/v3/stats/getScheduledResults'
HEADERS = {'content-type': 'application/json'}

# –®–∞–≥ 1: –û—Ç–ø—Ä–∞–≤–∫–∞ –∑–∞–ø—Ä–æ—Å–∞ –Ω–∞ –ø–æ–ª—É—á–µ–Ω–∏–µ response_id
def request_sender(metric):
    data = {
        "sessionId": ACCESS_TOKEN,
        "params": {
            "taskName": "stats-bg-basic",
            "taskParams": {
                "type": "basicStatsByAccounts",
                "request": {
                    "accountCodes": [PROJECT_ID],
                    "request": {
                        "dateFrom": DATE,
                        "dateTo": DATE,
                        "metric": metric,
                        "groupBy": ["date", "record", "embedDomain"]
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
    response = requests.post(url=SCHEDULE_TASK_URL, headers=HEADERS, json=data)
    print(f"Status Code (request_sender): {response.status_code}")
    print(f"Response Content (request_sender): {response.text}")
    
    if response.status_code == 200:
        response_data = response.json()
        if 'result' in response_data:
            response_id = response_data['result']
            print(f"Request sent for {metric}, response_id: {response_id}")
            return response_id
        else:
            print("Error: 'result' not found in response")
            print(response_data)
            return None
    else:
        print(f"Error sending request for {metric}: {response.status_code}")
        return None

# –®–∞–≥ 2: –ü–æ–ª—É—á–µ–Ω–∏–µ –¥–∞–Ω–Ω—ã—Ö –ø–æ response_id
def extracted_data_transformer(response_id):
    if response_id is None:
        print("No valid response_id provided")
        return pd.DataFrame()

    date_day, record_ids, embed_domain, project, value, uniqs, business_unit = [], [], [], [], [], [], []
    data = f'{{"sessionId": "{ACCESS_TOKEN}","params": {{"id": "{response_id}"}}}}'
    max_attempts = 5
    
    for attempt in range(max_attempts):
        response = requests.post(url=SCHEDULED_RESULTS_URL, data=data, headers=HEADERS)
        print(f"Attempt {attempt + 1}/{max_attempts} - Status Code: {response.status_code}")
        print(f"Response Content: {response.text}")
        
        if response.status_code == 200:
            response_data = response.json()
            if 'result' in response_data and response_data['result']['status'] == 'FINISHED':
                for i in response_data['result']['result']['data'][0]['data']['entries']:
                    date_day.append(i['labels']['date'])
                    record_ids.append(i['labels']['recordId'])
                    embed_domain.append(i['labels']['embedDomain'])
                    project.append(PROJECT_ID)
                    value.append(i['count'])
                    uniqs.append(i['uniqs'])
                    business_unit.append(PROJECT_NAME)
                break
            else:
                print(f"Task not finished yet or invalid response: {response_data}")
                time.sleep(60)  # –ñ–¥–µ–º 60 —Å–µ–∫—É–Ω–¥ –ø–µ—Ä–µ–¥ —Å–ª–µ–¥—É—é—â–µ–π –ø–æ–ø—ã—Ç–∫–æ–π
        else:
            print(f"Error fetching results: {response.status_code}")
            time.sleep(60)
    else:
        print(f"Failed to get results for response_id: {response_id} after {max_attempts} attempts")
        return pd.DataFrame()

    df = pd.DataFrame(
        list(zip(date_day, embed_domain, project, record_ids, value, uniqs, business_unit)),
        columns=['date_day', 'embed_domain', 'project', 'record_id', 'value', 'uniqs', 'business_unit']
    )
    return df

# –û—Å–Ω–æ–≤–Ω–æ–π –ø—Ä–æ—Ü–µ—Å—Å
print("Fetching daily data...")

# –ü–æ–ª—É—á–∞–µ–º response_id –¥–ª—è –ø–æ–∫–∞–∑–æ–≤ –∏ –∑–∞–≥—Ä—É–∑–æ–∫
response_id_shows = request_sender('videoStart')  # –ó–∞–ø—Ä–æ—Å –ø–æ–∫–∞–∑–æ–≤
response_id_loads = request_sender('playerLoad')  # –ó–∞–ø—Ä–æ—Å –∑–∞–≥—Ä—É–∑–æ–∫

# –î–∞–µ–º API –≤—Ä–µ–º—è –æ–±—Ä–∞–±–æ—Ç–∞—Ç—å –∑–∞–ø—Ä–æ—Å—ã (10 —Å–µ–∫—É–Ω–¥)
time.sleep(10)

# –ü–æ–ª—É—á–∞–µ–º –¥–∞–Ω–Ω—ã–µ
print("Fetching shows data...")
df_shows = extracted_data_transformer(response_id_shows)
if not df_shows.empty:
    df_shows.columns = ['date_day', 'embed_domain', 'project', 'record_id', 'shows', 'unique_shows', 'business_unit']
    print("Shows DataFrame:")
    print(df_shows.head())

print("Fetching loads data...")
df_loads = extracted_data_transformer(response_id_loads)
if not df_loads.empty:
    df_loads.columns = ['date_day', 'embed_domain', 'project', 'record_id', 'loads', 'unique_loads', 'business_unit']
    print("Loads DataFrame:")
    print(df_loads.head())

# –û–±—ä–µ–¥–∏–Ω—è–µ–º –¥–∞–Ω–Ω—ã–µ (–µ—Å–ª–∏ –µ—Å—Ç—å)
if not df_shows.empty and not df_loads.empty:
    df = df_loads.set_index(['record_id', 'embed_domain']).combine_first(
        df_shows.set_index(['record_id', 'embed_domain'])
    ).reset_index()
    df[['shows', 'unique_shows', 'loads', 'unique_loads']] = df[['shows', 'unique_shows', 'loads', 'unique_loads']].fillna(0)
    print("Combined DataFrame:")
    print(df.head())
elif not df_shows.empty:
    df = df_shows
    print("Only shows data available:")
    print(df.head())
elif not df_loads.empty:
    df = df_loads
    print("Only loads data available:")
    print(df.head())
else:
    print("No data retrieved.")
